{"image_id": "MGM_2017_page_54", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "NOTE 5 — DISPOSITIONS", "bbox": [143.8, 140.4, 397.9, 161.3]}, {"text": "On April 1, 2015, the Company closed the sale of Railroad Pass. At closing, the Company received", "bbox": [185.5, 185.3, 1094.0, 206.1]}, {"text": "$8 million in cash proceeds. On April 30, 2015, the Company closed the sale of Gold Strike and related assets in", "bbox": [143.8, 210.3, 1094.2, 231.1]}, {"text": "Jean, Nevada. At closing, the Company received $12 million in cash proceeds. On July 7, 2015, the Company", "bbox": [143.8, 235.3, 1094.2, 256.1]}, {"text": "entered into an agreement with Eldorado Resorts, Inc. to sell Circus Circus Reno, as well as the Company’s 50%", "bbox": [143.8, 260.3, 1094.2, 281.1]}, {"text": "interest in Silver Legacy and associated real property. On November 23, 2015, the Company closed the sale and", "bbox": [143.8, 285.3, 1094.2, 306.1]}, {"text": "received $80 million in cash proceeds and recorded a gain of $23 million related to the sale, classified within", "bbox": [143.8, 310.3, 1094.1, 331.1]}, {"text": "“Property transactions, net.” See Note 7 for further discussion of the sale of the Company’s 50% investment in", "bbox": [143.8, 335.3, 1094.2, 356.1]}, {"text": "Silver Legacy. Railroad Pass, Gold Strike and Circus Circus Reno were not classified as discontinued operations", "bbox": [143.8, 360.3, 1094.0, 381.2]}, {"text": "because the Company concluded that the sales did not have a major effect on the Company’s operations or its", "bbox": [143.8, 385.3, 1094.1, 406.2]}, {"text": "financial results and they do not represent a disposal of a major geographic segment or product line.", "bbox": [143.8, 410.3, 978.3, 431.2]}, {"text": "NOTE 6 — PROPERTY AND EQUIPMENT, NET", "bbox": [143.8, 455.3, 601.2, 476.2]}, {"text": "Property and equipment, net consisted of the following:", "bbox": [185.5, 500.2, 650.4, 521.0]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [895.8, 541.0, 1017.4, 561.8]